
"make" compiles all coq files

"make html" produces html documentation for all modules

"make pdf/CoursDeLogique-nfp120.pdf" produces pdf documentation for
all modules in one pdf file

"make alldoc" produces pdf and html documentation in directories pdf
and html. also produces a pdf documentation split in different files.

"make allclean" removes all emacs temporary files + other garbage

See details about the generation of the makefile in resources/README.
